</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_537_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ des Hanſen Troſpergs vnſer burgers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_537_r1l3">freunde hie fürbraht / vvie daʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> vnſer burger ir freunde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_537_r1l4">cʒu wyen in gefenknüſſe kumen ſey von ſach vvegen / die man auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_537_r1l6">Jn auſʒgeben hab / daran man Jm doch <expan>vngütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> getan hab </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_537_r1l5">tü </ab></add> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_537_r1l7">der vnſchuldig ſey / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ewr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade gnediklich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_537_r1l8">darcʒu vvenden wöllet / daʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ~ vnſer burger ledig werde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_537_r1l9">Als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan> / das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_537_r1l11">v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>durchleuht<ex>ikeit</ex></expan> <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> verdienen / 
