</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_537" id="268r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>albrehte<ex>n</ex></expan> von osterreich </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des Hansen
                        Trospergs, unser burgers, freunde hie fürbraht, wie daz der
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> unser burger, ir freunde, czu Wyen
                        in gefenknüsse kumen sey von sach wegen, die man auf in auszgeben hab, daran
                        man im doch <expan>ungütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>tü</add> und der unschuldig sey. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz
                        ir ewr <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade gnediklich darczu wenden
                        wöllet, daz der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> unser burger ledig werde,
                        als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan>. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>durchleuht<ex>ikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> verdienen.
                                    <add><expan>Scr<ex>i</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan></add>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v post <expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan> anno xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
